---
title: Fish Tikka Masala with Basmati Rice and Spinach
description: Masala curries are versatile tomato-based dishes that work with a variety of proteins and vegetables. Here, we're using a mix of cod, salmon and smoked haddock, perfect for soaking up the delicious flavour of the masala curry sauce.
